# React Native Architecture

- Prefer functional components with arrow function syntax.
- Keep screens feature-oriented and compose from shared UI primitives.
- Never use web router APIs (`react-router-dom`).
- Use React Navigation v7 patterns and typed navigation params.
- Keep auth-gated navigation split by app state (logged out/onboarding/logged in).
- Keep business logic in hooks/services instead of large screen components.

## State boundaries

- Local UI state: component state.
- Server state: TanStack Query.
- Global cross-feature state: Zustand only.

## Platform awareness

- Ensure iOS/Android behavior parity for interactive flows.
- Use safe area and touch target best practices for mobile interactions.
